細胞の代謝に関する基礎を修得するために、実際に、野生株、およびいくつかの遺伝子欠損株大腸菌を好気条件および嫌気条件で培養する。このため、培地の作成やオートクレーブ、遠心機の使い方を学び、細胞の植菌法や各種分析法を修得し、細胞増殖の測定や培養液中の代謝物濃度の測定を行う。また、得られた培養データから、比増殖速度や基質消費速度、代謝物比生成速度などの、増殖および培養パラメータを求め、細胞の代謝システム解析を行なうための基本原理を理解する。

This course will provide the basis on the cell metabolism. During the course, students must cultivate wild type Escherichia coli and its mutants under both aerobic and anaerobic conditions. In relation to this study, students have to prepare the medium for cultivation, and learn how to operate several apparatuses and how to assay metabolite concentrations. Moreover, student will learn how the growth parameters such as the specific growth rate, the specific substrate consumption rate, and the specific metabolite production rate are computed based on the cultivation data obtained. Some basic methods for the metabolic flux analysis will also be explained based on the cultivation data.

