Understand the basic metabolisms and the metabolic regulation of Escherichia coli based on the lectures and the experiments using test tube, flasks and bioreactors. The experiments start with preparation of the media and the set up of the fermentor, followed by the sampling during the cultivation, and the assay of the sampled culture broth and the determination of the cultivation paraeters. Finally, the metabolic analysis will be made based on the experimental data, and discussion is made about the current status and future perspectives fpr a variety of metabolic regulation mechanisms.

